headline: Unpacking Q4 Earnings: Kratos (NASDAQ:KTOS) In The Context Of Other Defense Contractors Stocks
summary: As the Q4 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the defense contractors industry, including Kratos (NASDAQ:KTOS) and its peers.
